                      </span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="/company/partners" class="block text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">
                      <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-orange-500 rounded-full"></span>
                        Partners
